item.description: Hi, I’m Rahul And I’m an Informatics PhD. student at Indiana University Bloomington majoring in Health Informatics. I listen to podcasts and read a lot of sci-fi. I’m tracking all the books I’ve read recently here, hopefully I’ll also start writing about those books. I also write posts about general tech stuff on my blog.
